#-*- perl -*-

package Unicode::LineBreak;

=head1 NAME

Unicode::LineBreak::Defaults - Configuration for Unicode::LineBreak

=head1 SYNOPSIS

Edit this file and place it on Unicode/LineBreak/Defaults.pm 
to activate custom settings.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Following settings are available.

=over 4

=item CharactersMax

=item ColumnsMin

=item ColumnsMax

=item Context

=item Format

=item HangulAsAL

=item LegacyCM

=item Newline

=item NSKanaAsID

=item SizingMethod

=item UrgentBreaking

=item UserBreaking

=back

=head1 SEE ALSO

L<Unicode::LineBreak>

=cut

